                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "9910f01b-532e-417d-87cb-aa8379ef9e56",
                            "text": "Look at the Portrait",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.showCloseUp",
                                    "imageName": "RitechezfirePainting.png"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "da3c2370-4127-4fb2-b44a-1ef31cbb7e08",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "\"Raphael 'Ray' Ritechezfire always wanted to be a hero. From a young age he was always off questing for glory. He enjoyed many such adventures. In time he matured and it become much less about the glory and much more about helping others.\"",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "980f13d4-ec9b-493c-a4ea-1ba90c71a813",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "\"Eventually the people lovingly coined the name \"Ritechezfire\" due to this paladin's zeal or \"Righteous Fire\" that burned deep within his heart. It's rumored that having such a strong sense of justice and compassion, Ritechezfire could never refuse aid,Â­ no matter the risk. Many believe this to be the reason for his mysterious disappearance.\"",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "0e78a014-401a-4161-a2c3-d4b74f5e921f",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "\"Ritechezfire's hope is that future generations of heroes can strive to do good for all persons. His legacy stands the test of time, and novice Paladins live by this creed: \"Love conquers all, but never go into battle without a sharp sword, a strong shield and trustworthy friends.\"",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "cc98737c-790c-45b4-a2b1-bc229de63ee9",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "What a hero. Maybe, someday, <i>I'll</i> get a chance to mysteriously disappear, too! Then they'll HAVE to have a painting of me up here!",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
